House Indorach is unique among the Dómnathar in having no Abyss Circle patron. They are nihilistic and atheist by Dómnathar standards—they believe in discipline, force, and their own capability rather than dark gods. This is deliberate and intentional.

### **The Abyss Circle (Nine Patrons)**

