Wind-Rider  |  The Wind-Riders (called Far Riders by the Pasua and Wind-Riders by the Mytrone of the steppe) are an ancient brotherhood of Mytroan lancers and Pasua mounted archers whose traditions predate the Deceivers’ War. They operate from the Gatefall Reach through the Eternal Steppe. The Wind-Riders intercepted the Lost Third in the Gatefall Reach and prosecuted the Running War across the steppe, remaining the elite mounted military force of the southern regions. Both names are canonical and interchangeable.

*The Staff Concord is a competitive SPORT at the Lament Games (Event #12), NOT a faction.*

